\b Clean the Greenwood [Thranduil]:\par
\b0\par
objectives:\par
1. Score some weapons at sites in Mirkwood\par
2. Invade Dol Guldur, Clean the Greenwood and do some Great Hunting\par
hazards: Elves\par
play tips:\par
starting company: Bladorthin (Trusted Counsellor, Elfstone), Legolas, Wood-elf (Star-glass), Haldir\par
- move early on to Dol Guldur, to play an item and invert Towers Destroyed\par
- then play more items in Mirkwood and Clean the Greenwood\par
- tap Thranduil to get Muster, Many Turns, The Hunt, Desperate Strike and Refuge to the discard\par
- sideboard The Great Hunt in to do some Hunting (use desperate strike to defeat creatures with body)\par
- sideboard Pass the Doors and Rescue Prisoners in near end of cycle, and move to Dol Guldur again to finish the job\par
